titles.title: MP1048 Great Is He Who's The King Of Kings

verse.name: v1
verse.lines:
Great is He who's the King of kings
And the Lord of lords,
He is wonderful!

verse.name: v2
verse.lines:
Alleluia, alleluia,
Alleluia, He is wonderful!

verse.name: v3
verse.lines:
Alleluia, salvation and glory,
Honour and power, He is wonderful!
